---
import LayoutC from '../../layouts/LayoutC.astro';
---
<LayoutC title="Subtle Somatics — Soft & Personal" description="Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics with Kaja Possert-Bienzle.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="hero-hi">Hi, I'm Kaja.</p>
        <h1>I help you come home to the wisdom already living in your body.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Through presence-based coaching and spinal energetics, we create the conditions for what is most alive and true in you to emerge — gently, in its own rhythm.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="#reach-out" class="btn">Book a free call</a>
          <a href="#work" class="btn btn-outline">How I work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-img">
        <img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Invitation -->
  <section class="invitation">
    <div class="invitation-inner text-center">
      <p class="inv-pre">I'm inviting you&hellip;</p>
      <div class="inv-lines">
        <p><em>to align</em> with the free-flowing rhythm of your essence</p>
        <p><em>to unfold</em> the luminous wonder of deeper aliveness</p>
        <p><em>to embody</em> the radiant expression of your unique creativity, love and power</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-card-inner">
        <h2>About me</h2>
        <p class="about-title">Unfolding companion, wholeness witnesser and integration facilitator</p>
        <p>I work with the natural intelligence of your body-mind-soul system — where sensations begin to speak, energy reorganises from the depth, and something deeply resonant starts moving through silent presence.</p>
        <p>My path has been one of deep personal unfolding — through layers of conditioning, protection, and habitual patterns toward something more authentic, more alive, more whole. This lived experience is the foundation of my practice.</p>
        <p>I don't guide from theory alone, but from a place of having walked — and continuing to walk — the path of embodied transformation.</p>
        <p class="about-german"><em>"Container schaffen, in denen die nächsten Generationen gut begleitet werden können."</em></p>
        <div class="about-values">
          <span class="av">Presence</span>
          <span class="av">Wholeness</span>
          <span class="av">Embodiment</span>
          <span class="av">Trust</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image -->
  <section class="soft-break"><img src="/images/kaja-secondary.png" alt="" /><div class="sb-ov"></div></section>

  <!-- Work -->
  <section class="section" id="work">
    <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:1rem">How I work</h2>
    <p class="text-center" style="margin:0 auto 3rem; color:var(--text-soft)">Two pathways into your innate wholeness. Both honour the intelligence already present in you.</p>

    <div class="work-cards">
      <div class="work-card">
        <img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" />
        <div class="wc-body">
          <h3>Subtle Coaching</h3>
          <p>Meet yourself where you are in life right now. Through deepening self-contact, you begin to encounter the vast resources beneath habitual patterns — courage, tenderness, clarity, inner strength.</p>
          <p class="wc-note">This is not talk therapy. It's an experiential exploration of what is present right now.</p>
          <a href="#reach-out" class="btn">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-card">
        <img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" />
        <div class="wc-body">
          <h3>Spinal Energetics</h3>
          <p>Working with the spine as a gateway to your energetic and emotional layers. Through subtle touch and sound, the body's own intelligence is invited to reorganise, release, and integrate.</p>
          <p class="wc-note">Many experience deep warmth and aliveness as the body finds its way back toward coherence.</p>
          <a href="#reach-out" class="btn">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Offer -->
  <section class="offer-section">
    <div class="offer-inner">
      <h2 class="text-center">What I offer</h2>
      <div class="offer-grid">
        <div class="offer-item">
          <div class="offer-dot"></div>
          <h3>An encounter</h3>
          <p>Truly getting to know the thoughts, emotions and sensations you have moment to moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <div class="offer-dot"></div>
          <h3>An unfolding</h3>
          <p>Experiencing your vast inner resourcefulness — strength, love, presence and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <div class="offer-dot"></div>
          <h3>An integration</h3>
          <p>Connecting into deeper coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem">Your journey</h2>
    <div class="journey-steps">
      <div class="j-step"><span class="j-num">1</span><h4>Discovery call</h4><p>A free conversation to sense if this work resonates with you. No pressure, just honest connection.</p></div>
      <div class="j-step"><span class="j-num">2</span><h4>First session</h4><p>We meet you exactly where you are — coaching, spinal energetics, or a blend. 60–75 minutes.</p></div>
      <div class="j-step"><span class="j-num">3</span><h4>Deepening</h4><p>Transformation unfolds over time. A series of sessions supports the gradual embodiment of your wholeness.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section" id="reach-out">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <div class="cta-text">
        <h2>Let's talk.</h2>
        <p>Whether you're curious, ready, or somewhere in between — I'd love to hear what's alive for you.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:1.5rem"><a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space" style="color:var(--blush-dark)">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a></p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted); margin-top:0.3rem">Online & in person — Vienna / Styria, Austria</p>
      </div>
      <form class="cta-form" action="#">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your name" />
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your email *" required />
        <textarea rows="4" placeholder="What's on your heart?" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn">Send</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutC>

<style>
  .hero { padding:8rem 2rem 4rem; background:var(--warm); }
  .hero-grid { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.3fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:center; }
  .hero-hi { font-family:var(--font-h); font-style:italic; font-size:1.3rem; color:var(--blush-dark); margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .hero h1 { margin-bottom:1.5rem; line-height:1.25; }
  .hero-sub { color:var(--text-soft); margin-bottom:2rem; font-size:1rem; }
  .hero-btns { display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .hero-img img { border-radius:50% 50% 50% 10%; box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(60,40,50,0.1); }

  .invitation { padding:5rem 2rem; background:var(--white); }
  .invitation-inner { max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; }
  .inv-pre { font-family:var(--font-h); font-style:italic; font-size:1.2rem; color:var(--blush-dark); margin-bottom:2rem; }
  .inv-lines p { font-family:var(--font-h); font-size:clamp(1.1rem,2vw,1.4rem); margin-bottom:1rem; color:var(--text-soft); line-height:1.6; }
  .inv-lines em { color:var(--text); font-style:italic; display:block; font-size:1.1em; }

  .about-card { background:var(--white); border-radius:20px; padding:3rem; box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(60,40,50,0.06); }
  .about-card h2 { margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
  .about-title { font-style:italic; color:var(--blush-dark); margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:1rem; }
  .about-card p { margin-bottom:1.1rem; color:var(--text-soft); }
  .about-german { color:var(--lavender); font-family:var(--font-h); }
  .about-values { display:flex; gap:0.8rem; margin-top:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .av { padding:0.4rem 1rem; border-radius:20px; background:var(--blush-light); color:var(--text); font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:400; }

  .soft-break { position:relative; height:40vh; overflow:hidden; border-radius:0; }
  .soft-break img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .sb-ov { position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--warm) 0%, transparent 15%, transparent 85%, var(--warm) 100%); }

  .work-cards { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:2rem; }
  .work-card { background:var(--white); border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(60,40,50,0.05); transition:transform 0.3s; }
  .work-card:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); }
  .work-card img { width:100%; height:220px; object-fit:cover; }
  .wc-body { padding:1.5rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
  .wc-body h3 { margin-bottom:0.8rem; }
  .wc-body p { font-size:0.95rem; color:var(--text-soft); margin-bottom:0.8rem; }
  .wc-note { font-style:italic; color:var(--lavender); font-size:0.9rem !important; }
  .wc-body .btn { margin-top:0.5rem; }

  .offer-section { background:var(--lavender-light); padding:5rem 2rem; }
  .offer-inner { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; }
  .offer-inner h2 { margin-bottom:3rem; }
  .offer-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:2rem; }
  .offer-item { text-align:center; padding:2rem 1.5rem; background:var(--white); border-radius:16px; }
  .offer-dot { width:12px; height:12px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blush); margin:0 auto 1.5rem; }
  .offer-item h3 { font-style:italic; margin-bottom:0.8rem; }
  .offer-item p { color:var(--text-soft); font-size:0.9rem; margin:0 auto; }

  .journey-steps { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:2rem; }
  .j-step { padding:1.5rem; border-radius:16px; background:var(--white); }
  .j-num { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blush-light); color:var(--text); font-family:var(--font-h); font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .j-step h4 { font-family:var(--font-h); margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem; }
  .j-step p { font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-soft); }

  .cta-section { padding:5rem 2rem; background:var(--white); }
  .cta-inner { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:start; }
  .cta-text h2 { margin-bottom:1rem; font-size:2.5rem; }
  .cta-text p { color:var(--text-soft); }
  .cta-form { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; }
  .cta-form input, .cta-form textarea { padding:0.85rem 1.2rem; border:1px solid var(--warm-dark); background:var(--warm); font-family:var(--font-b); font-size:0.95rem; color:var(--text); border-radius:10px; }
  .cta-form input:focus, .cta-form textarea:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--blush); }
  .cta-form input::placeholder, .cta-form textarea::placeholder { color:var(--text-muted); }
  .cta-form textarea { resize:vertical; min-height:90px; }

  @media (max-width:768px) {
    .hero-grid, .work-cards, .offer-grid, .journey-steps, .cta-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .hero-img img { max-width:300px; margin:0 auto; }
    .soft-break { height:30vh; }
  }
</style>
